<title>USA: Revlon expects to meet Q4 EPS estimates.</title>
<headline>Revlon expects to meet Q4 EPS estimates.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-10-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Revlon Inc said on Tuesday that it was comfortable with the fourth-quarter consensus estimate of $0.55 per share.</p>
<p>&quot;We expect our fourth-quarter earnings to be in line with analysts' expectations,&quot; a company spokeswoman said.</p>
<p>Earlier in the day, the cosmetics company, which went public in February, posted higher third quarter net income of $0.41 per share compared to $0.08 per share last year.</p>
<p>The stock climbed 7/8 to 34-1/8 in late trading.</p>
